        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Northern Border Reopening Transparency Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to submit a report on considerations relating to easing restrictions on or reopening the United States-Canada border to essential and nonessential travel. </p>]]>
